                  li Priority support
              
            article.plan
              header.plan-header.light-blue-bg
                span.uppercase.plan-name Fatty Pug
                h3
                  sup $
                  | 230
                span.plan-per-month per 1 year
                .plan-explain
                  span.text Billed anually
              .features
                ul
                  li.plan-views
                    b 1,000,000 views
                    .plan-explain
                      span.text
                        | A view is one page-load by a human. This is a soft limit, we will never shut off your site if you go over it.
                  li
                    b Unlimited blogs
                  li Unlimited transfer and storage
